com.adobe.icc.dbforms.obj

Class Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.icc.dbforms.obj.Field
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Field>

    @Model
public class Field
extends Object
implements Serializable, Comparable<Field>
    POJO representation of a Field in a Layout (XDP).

    Contains the display name, SOM expression, etc. for the Field.
